data.title: Snoop Dogg + Wiz Khalifa
data.meta_description: Legendary Long Beach rapper Snoop Dogg once again teams up with fellow cannabis connoisseur Wiz Khalifa—and this time around they’re bringing a few extra friend
data.text: Legendary Long Beach rapper Snoop Dogg once again teams up with fellow cannabis connoisseur Wiz Khalifa—and this time around they’re bringing a few extra friends, too. Too $hort, Warren G, Berner and DJ Drama round out the lineup of the High School Reunion Tour, which includes a stop at the FivePoint Amphitheatre.
